strings: <voice_0x01001628><se_def>exploding spikes: magnificent person! Despite several failed attempts to stop me, you continue to try, hoping to put yourself between me and my fate!
<voice_0x01001629><se_def>exploding spikes: However, his hopes were fading away. All will be lost in the end. There was nothing left but despair.
<voice_0x0100162A><se_def>exploding spikes: And the deeper the darkness, the stronger the flesh and blood!
<voice_0x01001627><se_def>exploding spikes: You are happy with me even with a miserable life!
